QuestData.Title: Deliver the Goods
QuestData.Description: Alright, $n, I need you to get this oil back to Fizzle on the Speedbarge, and let him know the good news!
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Barrel of Oil to Fizzle Brassbolts on Fizzle & Pozzik's Speedbarge in Thousand Needles.
QuestData.RewardText: It is oil! You're really proving yourself to be invaluable, $n!$B$BToo bad I'm going to have to send you off now.
